WITH 
approved_returns AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT ON (item_id) item_id, return_date
    FROM returns
    WHERE status = 'approved'
    ORDER BY item_id, return_date DESC
),
category_stats AS (
    SELECT 
        COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized') AS category_name,
        SUM(oi.quantity) AS total_items_sold,
        COUNT(ar.item_id) AS total_items_returned
    FROM order_items oi
    JOIN orders o ON oi.order_id = o.order_id
    JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
    LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.category_id = c.category_id
    LEFT JOIN approved_returns ar ON oi.item_id = ar.item_id
    GROUP BY COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized')
)
SELECT 
    category_name,
    total_items_sold,
    total_items_returned,
    ROUND(total_items_returned::DECIMAL / NULLIF(total_items_sold, 0), 4) AS return_rate
FROM category_stats
ORDER BY return_rate DESC;
